Game Design Document: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1UA5yExFgbCebrFAhKuBlr3UhojWS5UTS-3yW85ZjjC8/edit?usp=sharing

How to play:
----------------------
Move the car with either WASD / Arrow Keys
Collect coins and diamonds to increase your score.
Avoid bombs or else you will lose if you collide with them
You have a finite amount of time make sure to keep collecting the hourglass to continue to play

